七日七人車以下通過港豬澳大橋免過橋費,又無對中國人進港進行禁止及封鎖,將香港的肺炎感染人數大幅增加,將香港醫療壓力推行臨界點 -&nbsp;24/01/2020 至今<br />\n元朗西鐵站持棍傷人事件 - 2020/01/30(事件導致6名青年受傷送院)<br />\n<br />\n反送中運動警方行動紀錄<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=3b02a624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n「重開」又有香港人失蹤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755555</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有個 tg 失蹤人士channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/FindingHKer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFindingHKer&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=4db99a65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/FindingHKer</a><br />\n<br />\nfb group<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/434115767233839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F434115767233839&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=717b23ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/434115767233839</a><br />\n<br />\n￼大家仲記唔記得<br />\n太子站搵朋友個姨姨？<br />\n<br />\n831 搵失蹤姨姨 (之後有「認罪」錄音)<br />\n［勁恐怖］太子站前上鏡受訪問後<br />\n被逼錄音同可能已被自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577080</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xFrkHUZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxFrkHUZ.png&h=26b7fdb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TommyCheung0416/videos/397546497748719/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTommyCheung0416%2Fvideos%2F397546497748719%2F&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=3b226ad1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TommyCheung0416/videos/397546497748719/</a>"},{"pid":"203a886c89326f33bb92f17f23ea779e16937f3c","tid":1845